Package: fastfit
Type: Package
Title: Fast and convenient statistical workflows: summarize, screen, fit, visualize, and publish
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Paul", family = "McClelland", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "PaulHMcClelland@protonmail.com"))
Maintainer: Paul H. McClelland <PaulHMcClelland@protonmail.com>
Description: Fast statistical modeling toolkit built on data.table for efficient regression 
    workflows. Streamlines the path from univariable screening to publication-ready outputs 
    with minimal dependencies. Supports GLM, Cox, and mixed models with consistent syntax 
    for screening, fitting, visualizing, and exporting results.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://codeberg.org/matogoro/fastfit
Imports:
    data.table,
    ggplot2,
    stats,
    grDevices
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
